Fy_TheFortress
------------------

Some of you might now the basic map-design from the game **Crossfire : Rival Fractions**, an Online Shooter. The basic map was created for that game as a deathmatch map. It's fun to play so i thought it has to be brought to CS:S.

So here it is =), including radar-file.
HF playing and comment pls =)
